descriptionHtml:
Hailing from his home country of Morrowind, the Dunmer Ninja strikes down his foes from the shadows. Also being able to inspire fear into his enemies. The Dunmer Ninja is a force to be reckoned with.

-"You'll never be safe..."

This is not a mod, but a way to create your character. This is the first time I tried to create a build so don't be too hard on me. I tried different ways to make a Dark Elf but none of these kind of pleased be, until now! Behold! THE DUNMER NINJA! Lol. :P

So anyhow, please, let me know what you think about the build, if you like it I might make some more. :)
